WEBVTT

00:00:02.366 --> 00:00:07.820
(Zvuci prirode)

00:00:07.820 --> 00:00:10.536
Kada sam prvi put počeo da snimam
zvučno okruženje divljine,

00:00:10.536 --> 00:00:12.467
pre 45 godina,

00:00:12.467 --> 00:00:14.889
nisam imao pojma da mravi,

00:00:14.889 --> 00:00:18.368
larve insekata, morske sase i virusi

00:00:18.368 --> 00:00:20.496
stvaraju zvukovni potpis.

00:00:20.496 --> 00:00:21.939
Ali stvaraju.

00:00:21.939 --> 00:00:25.352
I to čini svako
divlje stanište na paneti,

00:00:25.352 --> 00:00:28.587
kao što je Amazonska prašuma
koju čujete u pozadini.

00:00:28.587 --> 00:00:32.161
U stvari, umerene i tropske prašume